body:
This looks like a bug in the storj library - there are > 600 copies of the drpcmanager go routine running.

Rclone is using `storj.io/uplink v1.4.6` which is the latest released version of https://github.com/storj/uplink

I looked through the change log for post v1.4.6 changes and I can't see a problem.

@calebcase do you think this is a problem with the `uplink` library?

@acsfer can you post your command line please? I'm interested in how many `--transfers` and `--checkers` you have set in particular.
